divs: sighting detailswhile riding in windrock atv park ( http:\\www.windrockatv.com ), my girlfriend and i was on top of a good size mountian enjoying the view, so she decided to take a few pictures. when we loaded the pictures on my computer to view them, it was the first thing i noticed in the picture!! neither of us seen it until we actually looked at the pictures! the even occured on 3-21-09 around 4:17pm eastern time. the first picture is the original picture, and is still on my camera the other two i have magnified a small portion and then inverted the colors on the last picture using windows paint (thats all i have) or know how to use. also!!! while looking through my recent atv pictures of previous rides on 6\28\08 i have another great set of photos, something that i had never caught earlier. there seems to be another one in one of my photos, one that did not show up in the next photo taken; no more than 10 seconds later.
